* Description *

hgformlogin is an extension to Mercurial allowing it to be used with
repositories protected by a form login. 

This could be the case for example when the repository is served via
HTTP on an internal server that requires authentication when
accessed from the outside.


* Installation *

Add this to your .hgrc file under the [extensions] section
hgformlogin=<path/to/hgformlogin/hgformlogin>

